snippet.title: Bullet Casters Early Access Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Subscribe now! https://bit.ly/2CVu6yi

Conquer 53 hand-crafted levels in the single-player mode or challenge a friend to the local PVP mode. full release of Bullet Casters is estimated to release in Autumn 2023 and will contain two additional acts containing new stages, enemies, bosses, and music and pursue the story set in the world of Silveris.
